casebody.data:
PALATINE INSURANCE COMPANY, LTD., OF LONDON, ENGLAND, et al. v. B. & B. STORES COMPANY, Inc. No. 953. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Oct. 10, 1933. Rittenhouse, Webster & Rittenhouse, of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellants. Hirsh & Hirsh, of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellee.

Before LEWIS and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

■ Appeal dismissed, on motion of appellants.
